{"layout":"timeline","root":{"data":{"text":"<p><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;\">实用青年心理学</strong></p>","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"456e3ffd-4b47-4bae-8152-2731227099d0"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 18px;\">第四章_应对策略</span></p>","uid":"1f6e5a61-1d3a-4284-bf08-322333a6d75c","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"\n      color: #749336;\n      font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: noraml;\n      font-style: normal;\n      text-decoration: none\n    \">应对的概念</span></p>","generalization":null,"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"da6029ad-3292-41ec-a393-5decfbdd23c5"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">什么是应对：处理压力而做出的努力</span></p>","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"6fad481f-e5ff-47b5-85d5-89d073c89195"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">应对的四种分组</span></p>","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"88ccd6fc-fad8-4d5c-9a86-8e3ffd10a7f3","generalization":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">？不理解</span></p>","expand":true,"isActive":false,"richText":true}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">问题聚焦和情绪聚焦的应对</span></p>","uid":"85b85c06-0bee-4c43-8682-4ed0cd0cbaef","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">卷入式应对和剥离式应对</span></p>","uid":"95b35d87-dfb9-476d-a4cf-5e7402317b1b","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">意义聚焦的应对</span></p>","uid":"10381395-0783-41ab-8aca-2e3342bb650a","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">前瞻式应对</span></p>","uid":"cf78edd7-8cb8-4ecd-b7b4-1496076d0130","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">应对的关键：最具适应意义的方法是灵活使用多种应对策略</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"6d8a1f74-70e5-42a0-bd81-eb3731e9e579"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 18px;\">价值有限的应对</span></p>","uid":"1fabae08-fc79-4dcd-b61d-8cc0f3069b6b","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">放弃</span></p>","uid":"b2bc2a2c-9029-4a3f-969e-133f2f21be11","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"generalization":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">目标调整的关键是：正确的自我认知</span></p>","expand":true,"isActive":false,"richText":true}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">什么是放弃：面对压力时，选择不作为，从这场战斗中退出</span></p>","uid":"320f316b-9ed9-4361-ac11-6c47707c372d","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">放弃的形成机理：习得性无助，即因为没有能力处理不可避免的厌恶事件而产生的消极行为</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"5dc0a6ab-1ce1-4967-bf95-fe4616645f23","note":"进一步理解：\n对于厌恶事件的认知和解释决定了人们是否会产生习得性无助。具体来说，当人们开始相信事件超出了他们的掌控时，就会出现习得性无助。               "},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">放弃也有积极一面：当你被指派去做一份自己没有能力应付的工作时，那么与面对持续的压力和自尊的降低相比，辞职可能是一种更好的选择</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"d0cb2fa2-6ba5-4a85-a70f-c7a5c2158600"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">对放弃的认知：放弃应该被称为目标调整，关键是人要对自己的局限性，能力和真正目标有着清晰的认知，避免追求不切实际的目标而产生的自我强加的压力，也要避免不做尝试的过于轻易的放弃。</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"9c9c15cf-6811-4e5a-8344-e8c6530711ab","note":"需要对自我有着清晰的认知\n"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">攻击</span></p>","uid":"c77d19e5-fc93-4893-a708-5fb3bb104eff","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">什么是攻击：意图在身体或言语上伤害别人的任何行为。咆哮，诅咒和侮辱比枪击和殴打常见</span></p>","uid":"04de5e4b-1110-4809-b595-3596cefec000","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">替代性攻击：个体无法对挫折的真正根源发泄愤怒的时候，很可能会将愤怒转嫁到替代对象上的现象</span></p>","uid":"83b5bef7-6862-40c3-ba8a-59e4a97b7844","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">攻击只有坏处，它不会缓和压力，宣泄情感。相反，它会激发更多的愤怒和攻击，而且会引发人际冲突，带来更多的压力。</span></p>","uid":"96e3a8cc-34f8-4f95-8ce4-8242036468ad","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵</span></p>","uid":"22d66303-e9ef-45f2-910e-2766352bded1","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">什么是自我放纵：自我控制减弱以进行替代性补偿。即:当你在某个领域不顺时，你可能会通过追求替代性满足来补偿自己</span></p>","uid":"ddfc307b-3d97-4e13-9879-89490fe06ec5","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵的例子：网络成瘾</span></p>","uid":"10c657b8-0432-4434-8698-377cfe00d9e5","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"个体因在现实中不如意而选择在网上耗时空度，获得满足来补偿自己。因此，当其不能上网时会感到焦虑，抑郁和空虚。然而过多的上网会妨碍他们在工作，学习和家庭中的正常表现。这进一步提升他们对网络的依赖程度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵也有积极的一面：一份热巧克力圣代可能帮助你在经历重大的挫折后平静下来，自我放纵的关键是不能过分的放纵自己，需要把握好度。</span></p>","uid":"c2242890-de91-458c-84f9-a684fa7c4efa","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵会引发矛盾的情感，因为一时的快感过后会出现后悔，自责等 其它价值有限的应对。</span></p>","uid":"e36d0253-9cae-40ec-97d1-f0ccc064621a","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">自责</span></p>","uid":"75618edc-c748-42fe-bb38-a19ce671e2d9","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">什么是自责：面对压力时，高度的自我责备。</span></p>","uid":"0be0f3a4-fc89-4818-9a85-d990ef984d8c","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">表现形式</span></p>","uid":"d23eee69-bbb5-4323-941c-387ca9711acb","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">不合理的将失败归因于个人缺点</span></p>","uid":"7ee277a4-93f5-46b9-a7c0-95877b66a295","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">注意别人给予的消极反馈而忽视积极反馈</span></p>","uid":"9a3cd274-ef62-4a27-b722-9f0fc7cb1c47","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">对未来做过分悲观的预测</span></p>","uid":"0df9a316-c470-4190-a748-e1329c85a806","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自责基本只有缺点，会给个体带来巨大的心理压力</span></p>","uid":"6541acad-4b50-47f8-b27b-539809a8da54","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">建设性的应对</span></p>","uid":"4aafb46f-5877-4948-9262-10bb78dd2c4e","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]}]},"theme":{"template":"avocado","config":{}},"view":{"transform":{"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"shear":0,"rotate":0,"translateX":-817.1937229437256,"translateY":-1344.7236652236659,"originX":0,"originY":0,"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"e":-817.1937229437256,"f":-1344.7236652236659},"state":{"scale":1,"x":-817.19